com.pvsagar.smartlockscreen.environmentdb

Class EnvironmentDatabaseContract

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pvsagar.smartlockscreen.environmentdb.EnvironmentDatabaseContract

  • public class EnvironmentDatabaseContract
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by aravind on 9/8/14. A contract class for our database. Makes it convenient to make dbHelper class and content provider. All the tables and the columns in each table are defined here. Make use of this whenever you want to specify table name, column name etc., to avoid errors.
